message.body: Hey - just wanted to check in and see if you still wanted to shoot on the 16th?
Hi! I was going to email you. I'm going to drive up to Vermont next week and come back on Monday the 18th. Is it okay to reschedule for September??
Of course!! Lets schedule over email and also figure out what we need. I come back from VT on sept 7
No problem! Have such a good time! You should take some photos while you are there for inspiration!
I'm going to do as much outdoor stuff as possible. I'll take a lot of pictures :)
